==Starting out==
===Inspecting Evil Dave===
* '''Player:''' Evil Dave? What's he doing on the secret council?
* '''Aris:''' The council is meant to include one dark wizard, but obviously the other members did not want to include anyone who was a real threat.
* '''Player:''' So how do I free him?
* '''Aris:''' To free Evil Dave you must make a stew, but it must be seasoned in a very particular way. The only way to find the recipe would be to ask someone who has tasted the stew.
* '''Player:''' But who could that be?
* '''Aris:''' Remember that from the point of view of the outside world, anything you do in here has already happened. All the people here are out in the world, because from their point of view you have already rescued them.
* '''Player:''' You mean I need to talk to Evil Dave outside the time bubble?
* '''Aris:''' Yes. He lives in Edgeville.
* '''Aris:''' With his mother.
* '''Aris:''' In her basement. I make no judgement about that.
* '''Player:''' Oooooookaaaaay....
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Aris again===
* '''Aris:''' Remember, you need to make a particular stew for Evil Dave. Speak to him outside the time warp, because from his point of view out there you have already rescued him so he has already eaten the stew. He lives in
* '''Aris:''' Edgeville.
* {{tact|end}}

